Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:09.20,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}満開の愛を載せて　笑顔  届きますように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:19.81,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}新しい世界の始まり　My Dear　Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:25.82,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,イージーだった私に　論外全部サヨナラ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:29.48,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}後悔なんで　もうしないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:37.56,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな困難なことも　ハッピーに変換したら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:43.39,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Shine  朝日も手招きしているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.34,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,不安にこっそり震えてても強がって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:49.37,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,胸　ギュッと振り絞ったら加速して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:55.36,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,勇気感じる　だって君がすぐ傍に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:03:01.37,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}一緒にどこまでも　進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:08.54,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}乗っちゃった追い風に　精一杯　届けたいからね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:13.33,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}君へと繋ぐココロ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:21.20,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}最新のコラムに　めいいっばい　気持ち込めたから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:30.02,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}ときめいて　どこでも行けるよ　My Dear　My Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:09.20,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}載上盛放的愛  希望笑容能夠送達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:19.81,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}新世界的開始  My Dear  Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:25.82,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經安逸的我  告別所有的不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:29.48,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}已經不會再後悔了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:37.56,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是怎樣的困難  也要設法變成快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:43.39,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Shine  朝陽也在招手喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.34,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,不安時偷偷地顫抖也要逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:49.37,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,揪緊了心一口氣全力加速
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:55.36,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,感受到了勇氣  因為你就在我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:03:01.37,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}一起走遍天涯海角吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:08.54,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}乘上了愛之風  竭盡全力去傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:13.33,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}和你相連的心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:21.20,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}在最新的新聞欄裡  將所有的心情都傾注進去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:30.02,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}心跳不已  無論何處都能前往  My Dear  My Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來來  吃飯囉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在吃了在吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夢  你餵它的該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係  我控制甜度了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是甜的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.60,0:00:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吧  文太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.63,0:00:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  這傢伙的毛是三色的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是母貓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.11,0:00:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你也給人家起個女生的名字嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像佳奈～這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要經過她本人同意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.81,0:00:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然不可能同意就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子長得就是一副文太的臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  代理已經出門了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊  我還想跟她一起走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.66,0:00:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為好久沒去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,估計她現在正卯足勁做營銷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,營銷？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.35,0:00:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,角鳥…各腸？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.35,0:00:56.91,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（「角鳥」和「各腸」發音跟「營銷」相同。）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:00:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:00:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都這時候了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要遲到了  要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.51,0:01:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要遲到了  要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要遲到了  要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.62,0:01:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要上學這幾天的早飯就吃麵包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.69,0:01:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣在新學期就能看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要遲到了  要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.03,0:01:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咬著麵包的少女～了吶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別一大早起來就喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶  今天是開學的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我從經銷店出發上學的第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然之前還在擔心會不會迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但多虧送了報紙  我連近路都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:02:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶  我好像很適應送報紙的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭  健君真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  之前健君的媽媽給我的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在哪家店買的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我媽媽自己做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  因為太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為是在哪家名店買的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:04:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我回去告訴媽媽  她會再給我們做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  健君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咲妃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我媽媽說想訂咲妃你們的報紙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎  那放學後我就去和你媽媽談談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊  我也去拜託媽媽訂報紙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趕上了趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們聽說你奶奶的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼我們能做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管什麼都可以哦  都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打鈴囉  大家都回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那等會再說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:04:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  大家看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有臨時的課  我先介紹一下轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是第二學期轉到我們學校來的久地院美華同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院  自我介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我聽好了  我跟你們是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  你們可不要隨隨便便就來找我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽懂了嗎  你們這些平民！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是啥角色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還能這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你要我們怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反而好萌～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是中町佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們認識？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  算是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是偶然在附近遇到過而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  所以要說認識的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算是伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伙伴？只是偶然遇見就能算？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別說傻話  誰跟你這種平民是伙伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朋…朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我才沒有平民朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說我說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同學的制服是白薔薇學園的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那所超有錢人學校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為什麼都在上白薔薇了  還要轉到我們學校來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼一說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前在超有錢人學校就讀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻轉到了便宜的都立中學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:55.77,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}（需要小心對待…？）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們學校的制服  也挺好看的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們到底想說什麼  拿我當傻瓜嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來佳奈  你帶人家在校內逛逛吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你還不知道學校裡是什麼樣子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有什麼事需要請教平民
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈你倒是可以依靠我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼不懂的就問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎  那…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼快就有問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想問的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這無禮之人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們出去買點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別忘了我要買的酒～哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒去學校了  感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是無禮之人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  聽不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈好可愛～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別隨便找個藉口就發情！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…來一次就好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就八次！就八次！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,次數怎麼增加了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再九次  再九次就行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平常不就這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說這個  我說的是你們大開著門在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被人知道我們這有變態  就會影響到訂單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  你今天收穫如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊  這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是代理  您營銷辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請問  營銷是什麼呢  今天早上也聽到過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是推銷的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,推銷是指推銷報紙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,報紙經銷店怎麼會推銷其他東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在小學推銷…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣  學校的孩子都住這附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟孩子們搞好關係了  就能和他們父母變得親近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就很容易讓他們訂報紙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要做到這種地步嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是基本啦  基本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈你既然來了  也要掌握完美的營銷微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,營銷微笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  你好好看著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  你試試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,眼鏡眼鏡…沒用的眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼說呢  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…這麼勉強你真是對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎？我不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪  到底哪裡不對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢  如果說這是普通的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.53,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,200)}（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:38.20,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}（尼波拉斯碰粘稠…泥淖）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尼波拉斯碰是什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正  經過練習一定能變好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以佳奈…別這麼掩面哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,練習嗎  咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:11:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這不是佳奈嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  又迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰迷路了  真失禮！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我路過這邊順便來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  有客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  這位是久地院美華同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是花日報紙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,花日？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是花日報紙派來的探子吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼呢  沒頭沒腦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是出來做營銷順便過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,營銷——！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是推銷報紙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你先過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同學  請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈  你聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,花日報紙在上個月末契約快到期的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搶走了我們十五個客戶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去問為什麼  居然是因為大米
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然因為他們會贈送大米就跟那邊訂報紙了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼啊  我們可不是米店是報紙店！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒米就給我去吃紙不就行了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣  佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也跟著去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去做營銷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日記～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳…佳奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日記
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來還真是夠巧的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈竟然也來做營銷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說是偶然  其實是代理她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈  你跟她一起去做營銷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後在她邊上陪笑  知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  但是我的微笑…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的笑容能成為強力的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:13:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,強力的武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的微笑不是不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你的微笑可是非常棒的笑容喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常棒的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有不行是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  所以鼓起幹勁去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  也就是說佳奈去的地方和我一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來營銷是和別的經銷點的人一起做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似是這樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,What？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要訂花日的報紙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同學  不行啊  這個人好像是外國人哎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh  花日newspaper？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他明白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:14:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  我是風新報紙的  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,No！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  下一家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,花日報紙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是風新報紙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要訂報紙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  久地院同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再下一家！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來  嚇跑的客人讓遙她們再給攬回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全滅了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢  久地院同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才想知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過大家好像都是看到佳奈的臉後關上門的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果…果然是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是但是  代理說我的微笑可是非常棒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大家一看到我的臉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪  奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是囉囉嗦嗦的傢伙吶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  讓我看看你的那個微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…上了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相…相當糟糕啊  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:16:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛  果然糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正反正…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼讓笑容變得不糟糕不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,練習下微笑不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢  代理也說了得靠練習的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  那麼就讓我來幫你一把也沒啥不可喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都跟你說了可以依靠我的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝  美華
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美華…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…醬…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你個笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准這麼隨隨便便的叫我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  美…久地院同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對啦  不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有  真是個漂亮的笑容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是當然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈也來試試
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛眯得太狠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是睜開得太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看著只覺得很痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,過來過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是哪裡不對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不知道該怎麼辦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是有點太硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  別動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同學  好癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都說了別動了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  已經不糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  這就上陣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,電錶轉得好快  肯定是裝作不在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無恥  讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的啦  這樣子會被罵的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你說怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,著·火·了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,著火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,著火了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有火災？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡著火了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火災可是哪兒都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼好吃驚的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放過了那麼好的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,練習的成果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是可以讓大家看看佳奈的笑容了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也…也是呢  難得為了我久地院同學那麼努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑了還真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別…別說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能為了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經八點了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的哎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點回去的話  大家肯定會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈  以後你直接叫我名字也沒問題喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說  我的心胸是很寬廣的吶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  美華
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  回頭見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈她  這不是笑得很不錯了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  今天我練習了下微笑喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,微笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,練習嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為  佳奈的營銷笑容可以說非常的糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭啊  佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  糟糕的應該是這傢伙才對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是努力練習過了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  讓我們看看你的成果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有哪裡不太對嗎  我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起白天的那個  好太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過話說回來  到底是什麼表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈還真是  太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:21:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶  我和大家在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.24,0:21:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得非常開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一話  「第一次的、游泳池」
