Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鹽味牛奶糖～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.03,0:23:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嚕～嚕～
